title: With 120+ News Publishers Signed On Google Opens Applications For $170M DNI Innovation Fund
text:
With 120+ News Publishers Signed On, Google Opens Applications For $170M DNI Innovation Fund 
Tech Crunch Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
: Google has put aside?EUR150 million ($170 million) for startups and others building new services, products and technologies for the news industry, and it will give out in grants twice a year, typically ranging from EUR50,000 to EUR1 million, but occasionally higher, with no strings attached, Google...
